title: Scp 8642 26
content:
You sit at your computer, clicking through the same choices, looping over and over and over again. Or maybe you're tapping through the choices on your phone. Maybe a tablet, or maybe some other device entirely! The point is, thanks to your choices, the player character is now in some kind of narrative loop. Is this your first loop? Your fifth? Your hundredth? Who knows?! Keep the loop going! Even if you go looking for other endings now, are you truly free of the loop? Does it even matter?

Congratulations! You found the Meta Ending! This is now a story within a story, maybe within another story!
